		<h2>Rentals</h2>
		<p>Renting in Spain is fairly straightforward. First, you can look for properties on the numerous portals where you'll find all types of properties; apartments, villas, townhouses, etc... One thing to keep in mind is that some properties are brokered by a real estate agency and others you can rent directly from the buyer, both have their pros and cons.
